title: The Shrouded Isle v1.0.2
description:
On a small, desolate island, a dark ritual must be performed every season. 

As the Archbishop, you must guide your wavering flock through countless hardships and bring about the awakening of the your dark god, Chernobog.

* Procedurally generated townspeople with odd quirks and dark secrets.
* Gorgeous painted art style inspired by Victorian era fashions and architecture.
* Haunting orchestral soundtrack that creates a foreboding atmosphere.

What's New:

Minor tweaks to audio.

More info:
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.foxboard.TheShroudedIsle
